{"tid":883013,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"檢舉直播台侵權行為，你我有責!","createTime":"2018-10-30T13:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T12:50:56.000Z","uid":193138,"like":9,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"110d2082dbde250ed534e9128bd6c909bf7aec7d","tid":883013,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢地D post用bot隔幾分鐘咁推 post係咁洗版都冇人理，<br />\n<br />\n侵權睇電影本身就唔係一件岩既事，光明正大咁播侵權電影緊加係罪加一等。<br />\n<br />\n雖然話就話個台唔係連仔到開台播，<br />\n<br />\n但佢地開連登猛咁開post去宣傳自己個侵權電影台，<br />\n<br />\n播一套戲就開一個post既時候，<br />\n<br />\n作為連打機都支持正版既連登，<br />\n<br />\n身為反盜版既連登仔之一，<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係應該阻止佢地繼續開post，唔比佢地繼續做埋依D侵權行為呢??<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廷伸網址: TVB 查詢 <a href=\"http://www.tvb.com/info/enquiry/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvb.com%2Finfo%2Fenquiry%2Findex.html&d=4yQ6pjSs0bH3JieQ0wn1pZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=31e4ae54\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tvb.com/info/enquiry/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"ed05c6693d4d1e82641288c397384ad49505b85d","tid":883013,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bb95729074f381bad9eb95e3ad81d95d9432aa","tid":883013,"uid":193138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548ad7f8494d838040f616c0b972be00e00c1319","tid":883013,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43e447f3a537aaec4814df2ce9d3fc48d45b3a2","tid":883013,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci